Changes made:

1. Added `extern "C" {}` before the `#include "aacenc_lib.h"` line to fix the undefined reference error.
2. Changed `const_cast<UCHAR **>(&start)` to `(UCHAR **)&start` in `aacEncEncode` call to fix the build error.